name: Day1 Asamoya #HENphoto365dayz
description:
Day 1 - Asamoya
Sunrise view from a sleeper train after a long hours ride. 

The train took off from Hua Lamphong Station around 6pm, and it was supposed to arrive at station(i forgot the name) probably around 5:30am. That sleeper train was the begging of Thailand Journey with my friend. So this is not perfect photo but it is perfect to begin with this project. I woke up bit earlier while my friend was still asleep. I still remember how I felt when I saw that view. 

#HENphoto365dayz project 
Mint a photo 7dayz a week for 356dayz a year. From 3rd September(Fri)2021 to 2nd September(Fri)2022.
